The evidence with the title 'Fact check: obamacare's medicare cuts | time.com ' says Aug 16, 2012  ... Since the Romney-Ryan campaign is hammering the Obama-Biden ticket on the Affordable Care Act's $716 billion in cuts to Medicare, it seems useful to put this figure in context and explain  ... The Congressional Budget Office estimates Medicare spending over the next 10 years will be about $7.5 trillion. 
